songs.title: Bicycle
songs.lyrics:
[Intro]
Yeah
She a fan
You ready?

[Verse One]
How does it feel? Are you enjoying your stay? (Your stay?)
Do not talk, let that new rise, but not right away (Away)
Grab that bike and let’s ride (Let’s ride)
To a place, you decide (Secide)
Somewhere that fits that vibe, collared shirt with that tie (Tie)
Happiness will arise (Rise), but please just let it be (Ayy)
Young kid, don’t rush nothing or nothing’s just what you’ll see
And you don’t want that (No), a place that’s so, so cold (Cold)
Where all the lost souls go, it’s such a long, dark road
It’s such a long, dark road
Baby, please, don’t go

[Chorus]
And you don’t wanna feel it
And you don’t wanna see that
So let’s go, so let’s go
So let’s go, so let’s go
Hey, hey

[Verse Two]
Now we’re past the beginning
We’re gonna be here for a while
Do you enjoy this feeling?
YOu’re gonna feel it for a while

[Chorus]
So now I know you feel it
And now I know you see that
And now I know you love that
Yeah, you— you— you love that
You— you— you love that

[Coda]
So let’s go, so let’s go, so let’s go
So let’s go, so let’s go, so let’s go, so let’s go
So let’s go, so let’s go, so let’s go, so let’s go
So let’s go
